<view class="container">
  <view class="header">
    <view class="sub-title">外挂加载完毕</view>
    <view class="tips">先求大同，再求大不同</view>
  </view>

  <view class="calendar-card">
    <view class="hooks">
      <view class="hook"></view>
      <view class="hook"></view>
      <view class="hook"></view>
    </view>

    <view class="card-content">
      <view class="left-section">
        <view class="year">{{year}}年</view>
        <view class="date-row">
          <text class="day">{{day}}</text>
          <text class="slash">/</text>
          <text class="month">{{month}}</text>
          <text class="weekday">{{weekday}}</text>
        </view>

        <view class="lucky-section">
          <view class="lucky-item">
            <text class="label yi">宜</text>
            <text class="desc">{{yiText}}</text>
          </view>
          <view class="lucky-item">
            <text class="label ji">忌</text>
            <text class="desc">{{jiText}}</text>
          </view>
        </view>
      </view>

      <view class="right-section" bindtap="openSimulator">
        <view class="game-console">
          <view class="console-header">今日重开模拟器</view>
          <view class="screen">
            <view class="screen-text">综合得分</view>
            <view class="score">{{score}}</view>
            <view class="comment">"{{comment}}"</view>
            <view class="attributes">
              <text>智慧:{{attrs.zhi}}</text>
              <text>财富:{{attrs.cai}}</text>
            </view>
          </view>
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="section-title">✨ 开挂上分必选 ✨</view>

  <view class="grid-nav">
    <view class="nav-card" bindtap="goToFood">
      <view class="nav-title">今天吃什么</view>
      <view class="nav-sub">三分天注定</view>
      <image class="nav-icon" src="https://img.icons8.com/color/96/hot-pot.png" mode="aspectFit"></image>
    </view>

    <view class="nav-card" bindtap="goToDecision">
      <view class="nav-title">Yes or No</view>
      <view class="nav-sub">七分靠打拼</view>
      <image class="nav-icon" src="https://img.icons8.com/fluency/96/tarot-cards.png" mode="aspectFit"></image>
    </view>
  </view>
</view>

<view class="sim-modal-mask" wx:if="{{showSimulator}}" catchtouchmove="true">
  <view class="sim-modal-container">

    <view class="sim-header-tab">
      <text>今日重开模拟器</text>
    </view>

    <view class="sim-body">
      <view class="screw tl"></view>
      <view class="screw tr"></view>
      <view class="screw bl"></view>
      <view class="screw br"></view>
      <view class="side-btn left"></view>
      <view class="side-btn right"></view>

      <view class="sim-screen-inner">
        <scroll-view scroll-y class="story-scroll">
          <view class="story-content">
            第一幕：崩溃与“叛逃”<br/><br/>
            连续加班第31天，你在凌晨三点的写字楼里，收到了老板对方案第17次的修改意见：“感觉不对，再找找感觉。”
            <br/><br/>
            这一刻，你身体里最后一根弦崩断了。你没有回复，而是关掉电脑，买了一张一小时后出发的火车票，目的地是一个你从未听说的、地图上的边陲小镇...
          </view>
        </scroll-view>
      </view>
    </view>

    <view class="sim-footer">
      <button class="continue-btn" bindtap="closeSimulator">继续</button>
    </view>
  </view>
</view>